source: src/stores/structureStore.ts
kind: module
purpose: Zustand store for loaded structure(s) — holds primary + secondary Mol* PluginUIContext instances, per-slot chain data (chains + secondaryChains), element data (primary only), activeChainId, primary + secondary fileName, loading/error state, editable StructureMeta, focusedChainId+focusedCategory for the Elements "Show Interface" interaction filter, cameraSyncEnabled toggle, loadTargetSlot ('primary' | 'secondary') for Library->viewer routing, and a monotonic clearAllSignal counter that components watch to reset state globally.
